title: Photos of the Week :  Origami Mosaic , Ice Web , Monkey Festival
body_text: The Loy Krathong festival in Thailand, a funeral service for Rosalynn Carter in Georgia, Macy’s Thanksgiving Day Parade in New York City, an eruption of Mount Etna in Sicily, hostage and prisoner releases in Israel and the West Bank, a greenhouse laboratory in France, an autumn-colored vineyard in California, ski jumping in Finland, and much more
